<emphasis bold="true" box="[1425,1688,3164,3197]" pageId="35" pageNumber="519">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1425,2552,3204,3237]" pageId="35" pageNumber="519" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="35.[1425,2633,2573,3237]" box="[1425,2552,3204,3237]" pageId="35" pageNumber="519">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1425,1560,3204,3237]" pageId="35" pageNumber="519">Breeding.</emphasis>
Pregnant Cadena’s Tailless Bats were recorded in May and November.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
