<subSubSection box="[148,904,285,318]" pageId="36" pageNumber="520" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="36.[147,1354,285,518]" box="[148,904,285,318]" pageId="36" pageNumber="520">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[148,383,285,318]" pageId="36" pageNumber="520">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Cadena’s Tailless Bats are nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[150,1089,324,357]" pageId="36" pageNumber="520" type="biology_ecology">
